General Config:

- Server computer running Debian
- Dockers for: Portainer, Ouroborous, HomeAssistant, Mosquitto

The basic config of sensor/response is over mqtt with the mysensors platform.
This was a super easy way to roll everything out into one cohesive platform.

Lights: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0769JZRKC/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_title_o03__o00_s00?ie=UTF8&psc=1
Flashed to github.com/stelgenhof/AiLight

Sensors: See individual folders in this repo
